## NFS mount rules for /etc/fstab

## Typical Systems:

citadel:/abyss/Media      /abyss/Media      nfs  r,auto
citadel:/abyss/Common     /abyss/Common     nfs  rw,auto
citadel:/abyss/Installers /abyss/Installers nfs  r,auto

## Privileged systems with full file system-write capabilites:

citadel:/abyss           /abyss        nfs  rw,auto
citadel:/abyss/Common    /abyss/Common nfs  rw,auto
